{"tid":895472,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"酒徒入面「幸福猶如流浪者，徘徊於方程式的「等號」後邊」係咩意思？","createTime":"2018-11-09T08:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T10:21:07.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbd337c8ee8537914a7da46e0c3c0f454e63096","tid":895472,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個諗極個意思都好似怪怪地<br />\n唔係太明白想表達乜<br />\n特別後半句"},{"pid":"375f76ed16c43b40ed02959253096688dc0b4c95","tid":895472,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"文學啲鳩up唔洗咁認真<br />\n<br />\n等我話你知<br />\n<br />\n「幸福就係一種食得好滿足，又唔係飽到嘔，然後又好期望下一餐，仲要唔洗你俾錢付出負責既狀態。」"},{"pid":"b60cb480e970c0b6e3de2750467ca882ac2a4c4a","tid":895472,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"我嘅理解係幸福永待追求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea91bd9b5acca940df5a9a7abe13b4e941df3976","tid":895472,"uid":19978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"幸福永遠都在流浪"},{"pid":"7bfb080730f74743342a0c0049321fc4ec3bfee0","tid":895472,"uid":21017,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"方程式等號後面即係結果<br />\n你只知道要追求「=幸福」，但前面個條式，要有咩input, 點樣加減乘除，你永遠都唔知。所以呼應番前一句：時間是永遠不會疲憊的，長針追求短針於無望中。<br />\n為左追求幸福，就只有無望不知疲憊咁浪費時間。"},{"pid":"ebedf55cc2fce2d814bd8adffdd1f1007ce76db3","tid":895472,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"你知道等號後邊就係幸福<br />\n但係唔知等號前邊係乜野<br />\n所以你依然唔知乜野係幸福"},{"pid":"1b416294df14ec7aa60d3be6f76a71cbd53e846d","tid":895472,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bfb080730f74743342a0c0049321fc4ec3bfee0","tid":895472,"uid":21017,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"方程式等號後面即係結果<br />\n你只知道要追求「=幸福」，但前面個條式，要有咩input, 點樣加減乘除，你永遠都唔知。所以呼應番前一句：時間是永遠不會疲憊的，長針追求短針於無望中。<br />\n為左追求幸福，就只有無望不知疲憊咁浪費時間。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d499cc5ea5ce34c92c0e53962ce9d177aaf2b9","tid":895472,"uid":50060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91bd4bbeb7d9503987b142c93eb6cdbe1c50a2e","tid":895472,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:04:06.000Z","msg":"簡單就係幸福<br />\n愈計較愈機關算盡 條式愈長愈複雜<br />\n幸福只係一個永遠都搵唔到嘅答案"},{"pid":"9b3bc903d18feb098e696a9cf0d926b5ac2d2629","tid":895472,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"流浪者成日冷親，要食幸福傷風素"},{"pid":"857c861addaf365aa39f7670262903b336e2a20a","tid":895472,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375f76ed16c43b40ed02959253096688dc0b4c95","tid":895472,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"文學啲鳩up唔洗咁認真<br />\n<br />\n等我話你知<br />\n<br />\n「幸福就係一種食得好滿足，又唔係飽到嘔，然後又好期望下一餐，仲要唔洗你俾錢付出負責既狀態。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"森巴比到幸福人未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410d96a9ebdfbf23a05a93986e7840c1f35f9c71","tid":895472,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"857c861addaf365aa39f7670262903b336e2a20a","tid":895472,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375f76ed16c43b40ed02959253096688dc0b4c95","tid":895472,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"文學啲鳩up唔洗咁認真<br />\n<br />\n等我話你知<br />\n<br />\n「幸福就係一種食得好滿足，又唔係飽到嘔，然後又好期望下一餐，仲要唔洗你俾錢付出負責既狀態。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"森巴比到幸福人未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T1